I am not sure, this is a problem or not but my simulation is getting stuck in one tick point. So I converted all ```always_comb``` to ```always@*``` and tried again and simulation worked fine.

I compared .vvp files and noticed that 

While vvp file with ```always_comb``` has following lines
```
E_0x55e8f4bdad40 .event edge, v0x55e8f50ed9d0_0, v0x55e8f50ea450_0, v0x55e8f50ed9d0_0, v0x55e8f50ea450_0;
....
    %file_line 12 112 "Event wait (@) statement.";
Ewait_7 .event/or E_0x55e8f4bdad40, E_0x0;
    %wait Ewait_7;

```
vvp file with ```always@*```  has following lines
````
E_0x55f64ad4ad40 .event edge, v0x55f64b25e5c0_0, v0x55f64b25cd40_0;
.....
    %file_line 12 112 "Event wait (@) statement.";
    %wait E_0x55f64ad4ad40;
````

